Cell["\<\
A device target from a native gate set, a qubit count, and a coupling map: A \
larger, linearly connected device: Once built, query a property \[LongDash] \
here the qubit count:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"419e1742-3659-4ce6-a72c-d43e78fd3b9c"],

